This is a list of characters from the visual novel, manga, and anime series Clannad.The main character is Tomoya Okazaki, a male student who became a delinquent after a fight with his father that permanently damaged the tendon in his right arm.omoya is the main protagonist of Clannad. He has been labeled as a delinquent at Hikarizaka high school, a young person who defies authority. He is the type of person who thinks deep thoughts about his life, but usually does not voice them out.
